   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Time Series Seasonal Decompositions\n",
    "\n",
    "Finding seasonal cycles in Time Series is a common task to perform. If a seasonality is highlighted, we may want to perform a Seasonal Decomposition of time series in order to extract trends and cycles.\n",
    "\n",
    "The Time Series Toolbox allow to compute such decomposition on DataFrame as for ECDF, Performance and Auto-Correlation.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Introduction\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "### Imports\n",
    "\n",
    "We import required packages:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import matplotlib.dates as mdates\n",
    "from odapi.connectors import Irceline"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from odapi.settings import settings\n",
    "settings.logger.setLevel(40)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Dataset & Client\n",
    "\n",
    "We load the dataset we previously stored and create the Irceline client:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "data = pd.read_pickle(\"dump/brussels_2014.pickle\")\n",
    "client = Irceline()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Decompositions\n",
    "\n",
    "It suffices to apply the `seasonal` method (which is bit time expensive), we chose a week for the periodicity as we are confident in the existence of cycle of this length:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "s7d = data.filter(regex='(NO|O3)').apply(client.seasonal, period=24*7)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Then we can unstack each component of the Decomposition:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "s7dt = s7d.unstack(0).loc[:,pd.IndexSlice[:,:,:,:,'trend']]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "s7ds = s7d.unstack(0).loc[:,pd.IndexSlice[:,:,:,:,'seasonal']]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "s7dr = s7d.unstack(0).loc[:,pd.IndexSlice[:,:,:,:,'residual']]"
   ]
  },
  {

   "metadata": {},
